# Job Service

Express API for job postings (DATA236). Week 0: health check, MySQL schema, CSV seed loader.

```bash
cp .env.example .env
npm install
npm run lint && npm test
npm run dev
```

Apply migration, then load Kaggle CSV (see `docs/job-seed-mapping.md`):

```bash
mysql -u root -p data236 < database/001_create_job_postings.sql
npm run seed
```
